  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Register as an organisation getting funding directly from the EU
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Give details of projects which may be eligible under the UK government’s guarantee for EU funding.</p>

  </div>
</div>

